projects.name: DOC-X
projects.description: Revolutionize healthcare with a website employing machine learning. Predict patient journeys, suggesting appropriate departments and wait times. The Clinical Decision Support System aids doctors by analyzing patient data, delivering tailored treatment advice based on demographics, symptoms, and history. Elevate precision in healthcare with this intuitive platform for patients and practitioners alike.

projects.name: Coin Change
projects.description: Developed a staking dapp with the smart contract made by using Solidity 8.7. Users choose which cryptocurrency they want to stake and how much they want to stake. The dapp then facilitates the staking process, which usually involves sending the staked tokens to a smart contract or designated address on the blockchain. Metamask wallet integration provided in the application so that it is easy for the user to connect to their crypto wallets.
